# Production hosts — LOCKED (Jun 2026)

**Do not invent or reuse hosts from old docs.** Some committed docs still say `CoreKnot-jfw0.onrender.com` — that is **wrong**.

## Read first (gitignored — not on GitHub)

**`.cursor/production-hosts.local.json`**

If missing on this machine: copy from `.cursor/production-hosts.local.example.json` and ask the user for values — **do not guess**.

